.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-SPENDABLE-PCT-STDDEV" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-spendable-pct-stddev \- FEAT-2787 channel-spendable-pct-stddev
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-spendable-pct-stddev
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports the standard deviation of spendable balance percentage across all peer channels (FEAT-2787).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN with key \fBspendable_pct_stddev\fR.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
